## Cleanup
To avoid charges, delete resources in reverse order:
1. Delete VPC flow logs from both VPCs
2. Delete both CloudWatch log groups
3. Delete the IAM inline policy then the IAM role
4. Delete peering routes from both route tables
5. Delete the peering connection
6. Disassociate and delete both route tables
7. Detach and delete both internet gateways
8. Delete both subnets
9. Delete both VPCs
